body:
Closes #2178.

This implements the remove methods of the `EmbeddingStore` for Qdrant.
It also addresses a few Sonarlint warnings for `QdrantEmbeddingStore`.

Integration tests have been added.
Thank you for the quick review and the awesome LangChain4j project!!
@florian-h05 easy and clean PR == fast review and merge :)
@langchain4j Are there any plans when the next release will be published?
@florian-h05 this week, most probably Thu or Fri
